Module com.example.form
Package org.uwo.cs2212.model

Class Layer

java.lang.Object
org.uwo.cs2212.model.Layer
Direct Known Subclasses:
UserLayer
public class Layer extends Object
This class is used to store data on the floor's layer, which is the type or classification of the various POIs that can be shown. This includes, it's name, type, text format information and if it is hidden. Each layer also contains a list of points (POIs).
Author:
Yaopeng Xie, Tingrui Zhang
